  <brief_title>Subcuticular Continuous Suture Versus Skin Staples to Reduce Surgical Site Infections in Colorectal Surgery Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective and Comparative Pilot Study Between Subcuticular Continuous Suture Versus Skin Staples to Reduce Surgical Site Infections in Colorectal Surgery Patients.</official_title>
